room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Make The Xscape in Statesville
room_description: The Cabin... You go out to the woods to get some fresh air, clear your head. Upon return to your vehicle, you discover your tires have been slashed and you are not alone in the woods. With no cell phone service, your only hope is to get inside a cabin you find out in the woods and phone for help, before they find you.
